node.text: Not bad for a Friday atmosphere 😃 look forward to more crazy loud energy from the Dutchies the next couple days! Gezelligheid 🇳🇱🇳🇱🇳🇱

node.text: Ahh yesterday was weird. Weather was relentless. Luckily this situation never happens but it was tough to take. Shoutout of love in particular to the fans in the stands. It was cold, wet, windy, yet still managed to see some shirtless with cold beers 😆 Thank you for being lovers of the sport and hanging through it all. Sorry mother nature wasn’t on our side to make something meaningful happen. Well, it’s a 200th race I’ll remember that’s for sure 🤷🏻‍♂️

node.text:
Where does one begin.. The joy, happiness, excitement you brought to so many TV’s and race tracks around the world may never ever be matched or at least not in my lifetime. I wish you the happiest of retirements but we all know that doesn’t mean a life without 2 wheels. Long may your passion continue. I’ll be waiting at your ranch when the seasons over 😁 
On behalf of pretty much the whole world, grazie! You’re a fucking legend mate. WLF
